Steps to run logistic regression examples locally:

0.Setup
- license
  # export LM_LICENSE_FILE=port@host:$LM_LICENSE_FILE
- substitute all $ROOTDIR below for the installation path of FCS_RUNTIME

1. Compile Spark application
- ensure Apache Maven is installed
- run following commands:
  # cd $ROOTDIR/examples/logisticRegression/app
  # mvn package

2. Start node manager
- setup Xilinx SDAccel LD_LIBRARY_PATH
  modify the platform.path, platform.acc.path, and platform.acc.kernel_path in
  $ROOTDIR/nam/conf/acc_conf/default as follows:
  platform : {
    path : "$ROOTDIR/nam/lib/xil_ocl.so"
    acc : {
      path : "$ROOTDIR/examples/logisticRegression/acc_task/LogisticGradientWithLoss.so"   
      kernel_path : "$ROOTDIR/examples/logisticRegression/acc_task/bitstream.so"   
    }
  }
- run following commands:
  # $ROOTDIR/nam/sbin/start_nam.sh
- check log file: 
  # cat $ROOTDIR/nam/logs/falcon_runtime_nodemanager_$USER_$HOSTNAME.log

3. Run Spark application
  # cd $ROOTDIR/examples/logisticRegression/app 
  # ./run.sh <train_data> <test_data> <#partitions>

4. Stop node manager:
  # $ROOTDIR/nam/sbin/stop_nam.sh
